---
import Base from '../layouts/SectionLayout.astro';
---
<Base title="About">
  <h1>About</h1>

  <p>Systems engineer focused on security infrastructure, adversarial ML, and bare-metal experimentation. This site documents hardware builds, evaluation frameworks, and low-level tooling.</p>

  <h2>Technical Background</h2>

  <h3>Areas of Focus</h3>
  <ul>
    <li><strong>Security:</strong> Adversarial networks, red-team simulations, VFIO isolation</li>
    <li><strong>ML:</strong> Jailbreak eval, toxicity probes, spiking neural networks</li>
    <li><strong>Hardware:</strong> PCIe passthrough, InfiniBand fabric, thermal management</li>
    <li><strong>Systems:</strong> Proxmox VE, IOMMU/VT-d, RDMA protocols</li>
  </ul>

  <h3>Tools & Stack</h3>
  <p class="tech-line"><em>Languages:</em> Python, C, Bash, Verilog</p>
  <p class="tech-line"><em>Platforms:</em> Proxmox VE, InfiniBand, CUDA, Linux KVM</p>
  <p class="tech-line"><em>Hardware:</em> Xeon E5-v3, Tesla P40, ConnectX-3, NETGEAR GS105E</p>

  <h2>Current Work</h2>

  <p>Building adversarial network testbeds for GPU-accelerated threat detection. Exploring CUDA-based packet analysis and RDMA attack vectors in the Hephaestus lab environment.</p>

  <h2>Timeline</h2>

  <ul class="timeline">
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-marker">
        <img src="/assets/flags/tr.gif" alt="Turkey" class="flag" />
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <strong>Istanbul, 2025</strong>
        <ul class="bullets-circle">
          <li>Built Hephaestus lab for adversarial network research</li>
          <li>GPU-accelerated packet analysis and VFIO experimentation</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-marker">
        <img src="/assets/flags/us.gif" alt="United States" class="flag" />
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <strong>San Francisco, 2024</strong>
        <ul class="bullets-circle">
          <li>Developed RedLLM eval harness for jailbreak testing</li>
          <li>Toxicity probes and compliance reporting</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </li>
    <li>
      <div class="timeline-marker">
        <img src="/assets/flags/jp.gif" alt="Japan" class="flag" />
      </div>
      <div class="timeline-content">
        <strong>Tokyo, 2023</strong>
        <ul class="bullets-circle">
          <li>Research on spiking neural networks</li>
          <li>FPGA acceleration (CREST-SNN)</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Contact & Links</h2>

  <p><strong>Resume:</strong> <a href="/resume.pdf">[PDF]</a></p>
  <p><strong>Email:</strong> [your-email@example.com]</p>
  <p><strong>GitHub:</strong> <a href="https://github.com/yourusername">github.com/yourusername</a></p>

  <h2>Site Philosophy</h2>

  <p>This site is artifact-first: diagrams, wiring photos, benchmark logs, and READMEs are linked directly from each project card. No marketing speak, no hand-waving. If it's documented here, it's been built, tested, and logged.</p>
</Base>

<style>
  /* Section spacing */
  h2 {
    margin-top: 2.5em;
    padding-top: 1em;
    border-top: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
  }

  h2:first-of-type {
    margin-top: 1.5em;
    border-top: none;
  }

  /* Subsection headers - smaller, less prominent */
  h3 {
    font-size: 16px;
    font-weight: bold;
    font-style: normal;
    margin-top: 1.2em;
    margin-bottom: 0.6em;
    color: #444;
  }

  /* Tech stack lines with italic labels */
  .tech-line {
    margin: 0.25em 0;
    line-height: 1.5;
  }

  .tech-line em {
    font-style: italic;
    color: #666;
    min-width: 90px;
    display: inline-block;
  }

  .timeline {
    list-style: none;
    padding-left: 0;
    margin: 1.5em 0;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    left: 8px;
    top: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    width: 2px;
    background: #ccc;
  }

  .timeline li {
    margin-bottom: 2em;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: 12px;
    position: relative;
  }

  .timeline li:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  .timeline-marker {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 16px;
    display: flex;
    justify-content: center;
    z-index: 1;
    background: white;
  }

  .timeline-marker .flag {
    width: 16px;
    height: 11px;
    image-rendering: pixelated;
  }

  .timeline-content {
    flex: 1;
    padding-top: 0;
  }

  .timeline-content strong {
    display: block;
    margin-bottom: 0.5em;
  }

  .timeline-content ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.2em;
  }

  .timeline-content ul li {
    margin-bottom: 0.35em;
    display: list-item;
  }

  /* White circle bullets for timeline */
  .bullets-circle li {
    list-style-type: circle;
  }
</style>
